title: Week 11 NFL Recap, Analysis; Lamar for MVP, Trubisky benched? (Football 11/18)
description:
Will Brinson is joined by Ryan Wilson, John Breech and Sean Wagner-McGough to recap all the Week 11 action from around the NFL. The guys discuss all 12 games on the Sunday slate including Texans-Ravens (2:50), Patriots-Eagles (19:10), Bears-Rams (29:45), Broncos-Vikings (40:15), Cardinals-49ers (46:00), Cowboys-Lions (58:00), Jags-Colts (1:05:15), Falcons-Panthers (1:15:30), Saints-Bucs (1:20:15), Bills-Dolphins (1:26:45), Jets-Redskins (1:33:00) and Raiders-Bengals (1:39:15).
